  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Mathematical Notation</h2>
    <p>Variable subscripts in mathematical sequences:</p>
    <div class="example">
      <p>
        In the sequence, a<sub>n</sub> represents the nth term,
        where a<sub>1</sub> = 1 and a<sub>2</sub> = 1.
      </p>
    </div>
